{"tid":1652942,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"吊掛救援「忘裝支撐掛鉤」!婦急墜40公尺亡 東京消防廳公開道歉","createTime":"2019-10-14T01:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T01:33:05.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"06658739846ea3f0392f1ffc20bacdabb64d2134","tid":1652942,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2VlzOZm0hFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2VlzOZm0hFk&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeNxdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=3535a258\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2VlzOZm0hFk</a><br />\n<br />\n日本福島縣磐城市13日10時許發生直升機救援意外，一名70多歲婦人自高空向下墜落約40<br />\n公尺，失去意識，並以心肺功能停止的狀態緊急送醫，目前已確認死亡。對此，東京消防廳稍早召開記者會公開道歉，坦言是忘記裝上支撐該名女子體重的掛鉤，才釀成意外。<br />\n <br />\n日本放送協會（NHK）報導，這起墜落事故大約發生在40公尺的高空，當時工作人員試圖透過吊掛方式救出該名受困婦女，但過程中卻發生失誤，導致婦女向下墜落。事後，該名婦女被緊急送往當地醫院搶救，並接受心肺停止相關治療。<br />\n <br />\n東京消防廳次長清水洋文稍早坦承，相關人員並沒有遵守一般情況下要有的「一人安裝、一人確認」原則，忘記裝上支撐該名女子體重的掛鉤，「對該名女性及家屬表達衷心的歉意。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bi3ojyP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbi3ojyP.jpg&h=de13bb11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8MpOsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8MpOsa.jpg&h=2491625f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbca5820cc0b3c0b424e34d582c0d0016ab71cca","tid":1652942,"uid":38143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:13:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def9c549fd6cd522a262576f710d72cb63e0b825","tid":1652942,"uid":85924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"係日本文化個消防洗唔洗自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8175fcd6f68ffceb85e71666e3f806f2b38148c0","tid":1652942,"uid":281932,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T01:17:30.000Z","msg":